    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你是食物。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为一只蠕虫——木星某个卫星深处的原生居民——你和你的兄弟姐妹、后代为人类提供了大量的蛋白质。是的，你们很美味。但你真的想被贪婪的人类吞噬吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283690/extras/7941b7e0912446989a3155145e41a3e1.poster.avif?t=1759055605\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283690/extras/7941b7e0912446989a3155145e41a3e1.webm?t=1759055605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏玩法</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《The Helminths》是一款线性平台游戏，背景设定在一个巨大的采矿综合体中，生产银河系中最美味的罐头食品。不幸的是，你就是主要原料。揭开这个工业综合体的秘密，蠕虫在这里被开采、加工和装罐。通过掌握精确的平台跳跃和解决环境谜题，穿越致命的人类设施，完成你的逃脱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283690/extras/ce47ea8e35bd8e1f0a267df2c1ce8008.poster.avif?t=1759055605\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283690/extras/ce47ea8e35bd8e1f0a267df2c1ce8008.webm?t=1759055605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>做猎人，而非猎物</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过独特的穿透身体能力，控制你遇到的每个角色。利用角色的特殊能力来避开障碍、战斗……或者将他们当作更高跳跃的跳板。无论你是悄悄溜过守卫，还是控制工人进入限制区域，战略性地使用这种能力对于你的逃脱至关重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283690/extras/ae27fa503090feaa5ec007e825ad9ce6.poster.avif?t=1759055605\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283690/extras/ae27fa503090feaa5ec007e825ad9ce6.webm?t=1759055605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过60个关卡，结合了快节奏的动作和环境谜题</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >控制每个角色，利用他们独特的能力</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在外星球的工业综合体中探索一个黑暗的反乌托邦未来愿景</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手工绘制的2D像素艺术图形和动态光影效果</p></li></ul>",
